3. Africa's Talking (SMS)
Go to https://account.africastalking.com/auth/register and create an account
After login, you land on the Sandbox dashboard (sandbox is free, no payment needed)
Click your username (top right) → Settings → API Key → Generate
Copy the API key
Your username is shown in the top-right corner (e.g. sandbox)
Update backend\.env:

AT_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
AT_USERNAME=sandbox
To test SMS in sandbox, go to Sandbox → Launch Simulator → add a test phone number there first (SMS won't go to real phones in sandbox mode — that's expected)
